equirements of this AD terminate after compliance with paragraph (b)(1) of this AD. Information collection requirements contained in this regulation have been approved by the Office of Management and Budget (OMB) under the provision of the Paperwork Reduction Act of 1980 (44 U.S.C. 3501&hyph;3520) and have been assigned OMB Control Number 2120&hyph;0056.
